List of statuses of the global program and how to move between then

status 0: Idle startup

0 to 10: all modules corectly started

Status 10: Idle wait, ready for opperation

10 to 20: start commando on webinterface

Status 20: Driving to the scan location

20 to 30: Arriving at scan location

Status 30: Scanning the glass

30 to 40: Identifying glass

Status 40: Driving to a possible bottle

40 to 50: Arriving at bottle

Status 50: Checking temperature of bottle

50 to 40: Temperature is too hot
50 to 60: Temperature is good

Status 60: Drive to dropoff location

60 to 10: Arriving at dropoff location
